task.summary:
Updated data connection to interact with API at account creation, fixed minor UI issues
Made DataConnection into its own class to be called outside main activity
Updated Search UI to make unused fields hidden for ranges

Changed data connection to pull all data into database, fixed date searches
Date searching was off by one month due to a difference in month designation
Called missing data load functions in the DataConnection class to load data into database
Changed account login to not allow user into app without connecting an account

Validated accounts during account adding/editing
If account not validated, gives user a proper error of which field is incorrect Added a new class to be able to clear errors on input text fields after the user changes the field

Created notifications to remind user to pray for prayer requests
Added several classes to help with notification setup Updated database to store notification alarms and missionaries Documented classes that lacked sufficient documentation Updated detailed views to avoid overlap of fields

Added Prayer Letters to app and rearranged some information viewing
Combined list of updates, prayer requests, and prayer letters Added loading spinner to show when server connection is working Moved viewing gifts by year from the designations tab to the gifts tab Moved notification creation to an async task
